		<textBlock>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text="Take steps to reduce barriers to participation and empower participants as you prepare for the workshop.">
			</text>
		</textBlock>
		<textBlock>
			<text
			size="18.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Bold"
			text="Why do this">
			</text>
		</textBlock>
		<textBlock>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text="Engaging people from all parts of your community is a must-have for success. Workshops are a good way of bringing people from different parts of the community together, but can also be difficult for people to attend. People need to feel included and comfortable in order to participate fully. Removing barriers and being intentional about practicing equity will go a long way towards productive workshops and building relationships.">
			</text>
		</textBlock>
		<textBlock>
			<text
			size="18.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Bold"
			text="How to do this">
			</text>
		</textBlock>
